== 正一千邊形的性質 ==
'''{{visible anchor|正一千邊形}}'''由1000條[[邊_(幾何)|邊]]和1000個[[頂點_(幾何)|頂點]]組成，每個[[內角|內角]]的[[角度|角度]]都是179.64[[度_(角)|°]]（約179[[度_(角)|度]]38[[角分|分]]24[[角秒|秒]]）<ref name="article swartz1993can">{{cite journal
  |title=Can existence and nomicity devolve from axiological principles
  |author=Swartz, Norman
  |url=https://ejap.louisiana.edu/ejap/1993.august/swartz.html
  |journal=Electronic Journal of Analytic Philosophy (EJAP)
  |year=1993
  |access-date=2022-06-20
  |archive-date=2020-07-17
  |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200717050029/https://ejap.louisiana.edu/EJAP/1993.august/swartz.html
  }}</ref><ref name="article jensen2014revisiting">{{cite journal
  |title=Revisiting Modal Imagination
  |author=Jensen, Ross
  |journal=International Journal of Undergraduate Research and Creative Activities
  |url=https://core.ac.uk/download/pdf/48853656.pdf
  |volume=6
