  }}</ref>{{rp|66}}，十分接近[[平角|平角]]<ref name="book herrmann2012number"/>{{rp|199}}，內角和為179640度<ref name="book herrmann2012number">{{cite book
  |title=Number, Shape, & Symmetry: An Introduction to Number Theory, Geometry, and Group Theory
  |author=Herrmann, D.L. and Sally, P.J.
  |isbn=9781466554641
  |lccn=2012019333
  |url=https://books.google.com.tw/books?id=b2fjR81h6yEC&pg=PA199&lpg=PA199#v=onepage&q&f=false
  |year=2012
  |publisher=Taylor & Francis
